The USB C to USB C 60W Data Cable Can Support Super Fast Charging, With Hundreds of Tinned Copper Wires on The Core, Which Can Charge 85% in About an Hour. NOTE：To Achive Max 60W Charging Speed, You Need an USB Type-c Port Charger that Supports 60W of Output.

The Tail end of the USB C Data Cable Has Been Specially Improved by the Factory to Address the Issue of Easy Breakage of Ordinary Braided Wires. Our Cable can be Bent More Than 20000 Times Without Breaking the tail end, Which is Very Sturdy and Durable. The C-Port Also has Good Load-Bearing Capacity.

reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the TAKAGI USB Type C Cable 3A Fast Charging (3-Pack 6feet) and have been thoroughly impressed with its performance. This set of USB-A to USB-C cables is designed to cater to the fast-charging needs of various devices, including Galaxy S20, S10, S9, S8, Note 20, Note 10, and even the latest iPhone 15/15 Pro Max with USB C Charger support.I noticed a significant 25% increase in charging speed compared to other cables I've used in the past.Durability is a standout feature of these cables. The use of strong fiber, the most flexible and powerful material, increases tensile force by 200%.This 3-Pack 6ft USB C Cable comes with an 18-month warranty, providing peace of mind to users.The TAKAGI USB Type C Cable 3A Fast Charging is a reliable and efficient solution for all your charging and data transfer needs. Its fast charging capabilities, safety certifications, enhanced durability, and broad device compatibility make it a valuable addition to any tech enthusiast's collection.
